          <li class="dropdown">
            <a href="login" class="dropbtn">Account</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="advisory-hero">
      <h1>ADVISORIES</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="card-40">
        <div class="card-header-light">
          <center>
            <p>
              WEATHER REPORT
              <img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios/50/FFFFFF/error--v1.png" />
            </p>
          </center>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body-dark">
          <p>
            Partly cloudy skies with isolated rain showers will be experienced
            throughout Brgy. Pulang Lupa Dos and Brgy Manuyo Dos. Chance of rain
            is low throughout the day.
          </p>
          <p>Temperature Ranges from 26 to 31 Degrees Celsius</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-60">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header-dark">
              <img
                src="img/image.png"
                style="
                  width: 15%;
                  height: 65%;
                  padding-right: 20px;
                  padding-top: 10px;
                "
                alt="logo"
              />
              <center>
                <p>WEATHER REPORT</p>
                <p class="small">
                  Las Pi√±as City Disaster Risk Reduction Management Council
                </p>
              </center>
              <img
                src="img/triangle-logo.png"
                style="
                  width: 15%;
                  height: 60%;
                  padding-left: 20px;
                  padding-top: 15px;
                "
                alt="triangle-logo"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="card-body-light">
              <h1>WHAT TO DO BEFORE A TYPHOON?</h1>
              <ol>
                <li>Listen to weather updates and advisories.</li>
                <li>
                  Keep watch for warnings and plans regarding evacuation in your
                  community.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Check your house's condition and make necessary repairs.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Prepare a survival kit. (emergency items such as canned goods,
                  water and first aid kits)
                </li>
                <li>
                  Keep your survival kit in an area where you can easily get it
                  in case of emergency.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Evacuate immediately once asked by the authorities to do so
                </li>
              </ol>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-40">
          <div class="card-blue">
            <h2>Color-Coded</h2>
            <h2>Rainfall Advisories</h2>
            <table>
              <tr class="code bg-red">
                <td style="width: 20%">
                  <img
                    src="https://img.icons8.com/ios/50/FFFFFF/torrential-rain--v1.png"
                  />
                </td>
                <td style="width: 40%; text-align: center">
                  <p>Serious Flooding expected in low lying areas</p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 30%">
                  <h2>EVACUATE</h2>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="code bg-orange">
                <td style="width: 20%">
                  <img
                    src="https://img.icons8.com/ios/50/FFFFFF/torrential-rain--v1.png"
                  />
                </td>
                <td style="width: 40%; text-align: center">
                  <p>Serious Flooding expected in low lying areas</p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 30%">
                  <h2>ALERT</h2>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="code bg-yellow">
                <td style="width: 20%">
                  <img
                    src="https://img.icons8.com/ios/50/FFFFFF/torrential-rain--v1.png"
                  />
                </td>
                <td style="width: 40%; text-align: center">
                  <p>Serious Flooding expected in low lying areas</p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 30%">
                  <h2>MONITOR</h2>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="code bg-green">
                <td style="width: 20%">
                  <img
                    src="https://img.icons8.com/dotty/80/FFFFFF/clouds.png"
                  />
                </td>
                <td style="width: 40%; text-align: center">
                  <p>Serious Flooding expected in low lying areas</p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 30%">
                  <h2>NO ALERT</h2>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="right">
      <img src="img/image.png" style="width: 50px" alt="logo" />
      <img
        src="img/triangle-logo.png"
        style="width: 50px"
        alt="triangle-logo"
      />
    </div>

    <script src="js/index.js"></script>
